{"tid":435120,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想死既人會唔會寫好晒遺書先走","createTime":"2017-10-14T03:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T01:45:32.000Z","uid":59569,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd01fb693d4f2fcd91422e00e39bf88392e2574","tid":435120,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"由四月諗到依家都未敢去試<br />\n最多都係開左窗坐喺邊邊到<br />\n<br />\n發生左好多事，我又唔識處理<br />\n記得有晚我發燒燒到全身都冇力<br />\n打俾老豆問佢可唔可以送我去醫院<br />\n（屋企長期得我一個）<br />\n佢話叫我自己飲多d水<br />\n訓醒就冇事<br />\n個刻以為自己真係會死<br />\n第朝迷迷糊糊咁先拖落街睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n每次對人生有返希望個陣<br />\n轉頭又跌返落谷底<br />\nd人自己拍緊拖，就同你講人生唔係得愛情<br />\n讀書好勁就話其實讀完出黎做野都係咁<br />\n做緊正苦工既就輕輕鬆鬆<br />\n<br />\n幾時先可以唔俾命運控制"},{"pid":"97e1546f555ec4fd7fc5a8f8f8688646f710b5c1","tid":435120,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2b7ee6ef9a526bb91820dc29a17a29c85fb0c0","tid":435120,"uid":152080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"家庭問題定係點？慢慢組織下語言 講出黎會舒服D<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2862e2e0445147ad24df7222045291d1956f38e2","tid":435120,"uid":74455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"有冇想為佢而努力既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16757e91a9a51ff6ecd7b02da03bb70ecb4d1d45","tid":435120,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"就算我點努力都改變唔到<br />\n成日諗係咪好多野都係整定"},{"pid":"651e1374cb396a17121ebe4979b1d2a7c00aa5eb","tid":435120,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"攬住我"},{"pid":"a169ad191c2a8230050c572ef8ec91232c09706d","tid":435120,"uid":1378